creator: atertop
descriptionHtml:
Atertop displays your profile on the main page for one hour, giving you the opportunity to be noticed when you post great contents.

Atertop is a location based platform, where you can see what is going on in your area or any area in the world ( city, region, country ).

The concept of subzone introduced by atertop allows you to target people from or interested in a certain country and living in a given area. For example you can target Brazilians living in Montreal with your contents by selecting Montreal as zone and Brazil as subzone.

When content is published, users can vote whether it is cool, serious or useful. Then every hour, the 3 profiles with the best contents in the 3 categories are displayed on the main page for one hour granting them with great awareness.

- You can share pictures, texts, videos in your area or in any area in the world
- You can be top on different level, top in the city, top in the region or top in the country by sharing in those areas. The more the level is high, the more it is valuable.
- Your profile indicates your status, whether you are cool ; serious or useful given the reactions of users about the contents that you share.
- Your profile also indicates your statistics
- You can switch your feed from a zone to the accounts that you follow
- You can access the top profiles from the previous hours in the tops summary

Do you have questions, problems or comments? Visit www.atertop.com/contact/
